high_descs: Walk near the sofa, take left and walk towards the TV stand.
Take the spoon from the TV stand.
Turn right, take left near the fridge  and walk towards the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink, wash it and take it.
Keep the spoon near the sink.
anns.task_desc: To wash the spoon and keep it near the sink.

high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the tv stand on your right
Pick up spoon from the tv stand
Head straight towards the sink by turning around and turning left
Place spoon inside the sink and then take it out
anns.task_desc: Washing spoon on the sink and placing it on sink

high_descs: Take the spoon in the table
Put the spoon in the sink, clean it off
Place the spoon on the sink
anns.task_desc: Take the spoon in the table Place the spoon on the sink
